title: Barclays Computers (PVT) Ltd. - CD POUCH- - CD Sleeves PPD-2P (N/W)
specs: If you have many CDs or DVDs in your home, you'd better pay attention to this useful disc paper sleeve which can help you put all CDs/DVDs in order. This disc paper sleeve is made of high quality, durable for a long time use. Featured with a protective outer shell, it can keep discs safe and shield them from extreme temperatures. What's more, it features large capacity, ideal for storing your media from dust and scrapes. With compact size, this disc paper sleeve is easy to install and remove, thus you can take it along with you to anywhere. What a great disc paper sleeve, it will bring you much convenience!
